# CORS allowlist. Comma-separated, exact match, no trailing slashes.
# Default "*" allows any origin (fine for local dev).
# In production set to your frontend URL(s), e.g.:
#   ALLOWED_ORIGINS=https://causal-tutor.vercel.app
#   ALLOWED_ORIGINS=https://causal-tutor.vercel.app,https://tutor.yourlab.org
ALLOWED_ORIGINS=*
